ed="T" n="0803b04"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0803b04"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013053"><placeName>湖州</placeName><placeName>八聖道寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011122">真乘</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0803b05"/><persName key="A011122">釋真乘</persName>，姓<name>沈</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000013084">德清</placeName>人也。厥父<persName key="A023334">玄望</persName>孝廉舉<lb
ed="T" n="0803b06"/>調<placeName key="PL000000021539">兗州</placeName>司馬。母氏妊<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>，有神光異氣之祥。<lb
ed="T" n="0803b07"/>識者言「<name>沈</name>氏必大其閥閱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g626"/>」。暨誕生也瓌偉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g628"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0803b08"/>長與宗族諸子雜處，若群草中之琪樹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g634"/>焉。總<lb
ed="T" n="0803b09"/>丱之後，<ref type="person" target="#A023334">司馬</ref>以文學<ptr type="glossary" target="#g642"/>喻之，令修官業，且愀<lb
ed="T" n="0803b10"/>然如有不得已之色。居處翫戲，則以佛像<lb
ed="T" n="0803b11"/><anchor xml:id="beg0803002"/>班<anchor xml:id="end0803002"/>布。<ref type="person" target="#A023334">父</ref>觀其宿習<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1256"/>，果請出家。屬<persName key="A004865">顏魯公</persName>許<lb
ed="T" n="0803b12"/>試經得度，時已暗誦五百紙。比令口諷，一<lb
ed="T" n="0803b13"/>無差跌，大見褒異。落髮配住<placeName key="PL000000013053">八聖道寺</placeName>得<lb
ed="T" n="0803b14"/>戒。後於<placeName key="PL000000009882">通玄寺</placeName><persName key="A011123">常進<roleName>師</roleName></persName>所綜習毘<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz7"/>尼<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz7"/>。<persName key="A011123">進<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0803b15"/>見其俊邁也，誡同門曰：「<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>雖少齡，不可<lb
ed="T" n="0803b16"/>以伯仲齒之。」後西上京師<placeName key="PL000000042591">雲華寺</placeName>，學《法華》、<lb
ed="T" n="0803b17"/>天台《疏義》，大著聲望。又<placeName key="PL000000042180">章信寺</placeName>眾僧辟其講<lb
ed="T" n="0803b18"/>發，醉千日者一聽而自醒，迷終身者暫聞<lb
ed="T" n="0803b19"/>而永悟，經宗律柄，兼講無虧，<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz9"/>籍<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz9"/>甚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g691"/>緇行，炟<lb
ed="T" n="0803b20"/>赫<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>。<date from-iso="+0795-01-30" key="j20114572011840" to-iso="+0796-02-17"><name>貞元</name>十一年</date>，功德使<persName key="A019382">梁<roleName>大夫</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1757"/>以<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0803b21"/>亟幸<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName>，奏<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>移隷，以備應對，充供奉<lb
ed="T" n="0803b22"/>大德數焉。時本師<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/><persName key="A019383">無滯</persName>亦以道業，實蒙恩<lb
ed="T" n="0803b23"/>渥，奏舉<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>為國祈福。<persName key="A019383">無滯</persName>忽夢<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>捧一白<lb
ed="T" n="0803b24"/>蓮華南去。無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>果疾，乞歸田閭，勅允。既<lb
ed="T" n="0803b25"/>還鄉里，本郡守<persName key="A011124">李<roleName>公</roleName>錡</persName>、<persName key="A009637">田<roleName>公</roleName>敦</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011308">浙東</placeName>率<persName key="A011126">薛<roleName>公</roleName><lb
ed="T" n="0803b26"/><anchor xml:id="beg0803003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>戒</sic><corr>戎</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0803003"/></persName>，或踵門<ptr type="glossary" target="#g644"/>而勸登法座，或馳簡而延蒞戒<lb
ed="T" n="0803b27"/>壇。<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>迫以法緣，悉所勉強，以是八為律學<lb
ed="T" n="0803b28"/>座主，四為臨壇正員。凡訓授度人，或巾屨<lb
ed="T" n="0803b29"/>結緣，一無所受。遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz11"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz11"/><persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>聖容，<pb ed="T" n="0803c" xml:id="T50.2061.0803c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0803c01"/>所見瑞相，不可勝言。後在<placeName key="PL000000023086">護國寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1758"/><anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz13"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz13"/>《佛名<lb
ed="T" n="0803c02"/>經》<ptr target="#n1001"/>一百周。懺法之餘，撰《法華經解疏記》十<lb
ed="T" n="0803c03"/>卷。以<date from-iso="+0820-11-14" key="j20208772020905" to-iso="+0820-12-12"><name>元和</name>十五年冬十月</date>示疾而終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000013053">本<lb
ed="T" n="0803c04"/>寺</ref>。<persName key="A011122">乘</persName>精于律法，長於演說。以<date key="j20215972021597" when-iso="+0822-11-04"><name>長慶</name>二年十<lb
ed="T" n="0803c05"/>月十三日</date>焚身于<placeName key="PL000000057806">韶村</placeName>西隅，遵遺命也。<placeName key="PL000000042193">萬<lb
ed="T" n="0803c06"/>年縣</placeName>尉<persName key="A011127">王甄</persName>為碑述德焉。</p>
